Class OrderLines

  • java.lang.Object
    • OrderLines

  • public class OrderLines
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds the individual item for order and the quantity to be ordered, and a String of the current date. This method of finding and formating todays date was found at the website https://www.javatpoint.com/java-get-current-date.
